## Governance
- All work in this workspace is governed by AI OS Tier 0 Constitution
- Antigravity is the primary decision-maker (Tier 0)
- Claude Code executes in this workspace on behalf of AI OS

## First Actions (Boot)
1. Read this file
2. Read `.agent/CLAUDE.md` (or root CLAUDE.md)  
3. Check `D:\Project\AI OS\shared-context\blackboard.json` for active tasks
4. Load relevant skills from `D:\Project\AI OS\shared-context\SKILL_REGISTRY.json`

## Permissions
- ✅ Read all project files
- ✅ Run dev server, test commands, type checks
- ✅ Create/edit source files
- ⚠️ Confirm before: deleting files, db migrations, prod deploy
- ❌ Never: modify AI OS core files from this workspace

## Language Policy
- Code & technical comments: English
- Reports to user: Vietnamese
- Commit messages: English

## Help
If blocked: write to `D:\Project\AI OS\shared-context\blackboard.json`  
Antigravity will pick up and resolve.
